Megatron puts on a burst of speed seeing the blasts come at him, and he
quickly levels up about them, also uknowingly avoiding Scyther's attack
and sending the 25 bullets on to him (hot potato).

He then scans around and sees Switchblade sneaking off. He would have to
chat with him later about this annoying agenda of his. But more
interesting was the Damaged Iron Raptor. He had so wanted to deal with
her personally, but, he knew to take and opportunity when the chance
came. He aimed his fusion cannon downwards, and took aim on Iron Raptor,
and let loose the torrent of pink energy, the blast's power pushing him
higher upwards, as the stream headed straight for Iron Raptor.
